00:36:33,930 --> 00:36:38,480
Our web store and short advertising videos will be our major sales channels.

484
00:36:38,480 --> 00:36:40,050
Great.

485
00:36:41,010 --> 00:36:43,410
I'm not good at all these, so I'll leave them in your hands.

486
00:36:43,410 --> 00:36:45,920
- We'll do as you say.
- All right?

487
00:36:48,110 --> 00:36:49,440
Done with the filming?

488
00:36:49,440 --> 00:36:51,380
- Let's head outside.
- Sure.

489
00:36:51,380 --> 00:36:52,820
Come on.

490
00:36:57,900 --> 00:37:01,090
Xia Xia! Come over here.

491
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:04,880
