493
00:37:06,900 --> 00:37:08,990
I do, but I have very few viewers.

494
00:37:08,990 --> 00:37:11,560
It's okay. We were there once.

495
00:37:11,560 --> 00:37:13,410
Sit down.

496
00:37:14,400 --> 00:37:15,960
I've talked to Uncle.

497
00:37:15,960 --> 00:37:17,950
You should continue with your live streaming.

498
00:37:17,950 --> 00:37:21,570
In addition, Xiao Yue has also registered multiple accounts for the wood carving workshop.

499
00:37:21,570 --> 00:37:24,470
She'll come over occasionally to make short videos.

500
00:37:24,470 --> 00:37:28,400
She also planned a master-apprentice series for you two.

501
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:31,490
- You can film your master.
- Okay.

502
00:37:31,490 --> 00:37:34,160
Wait, no. I don't want to be filmed. Why are you filming me?

503
00:37:34,160 --> 00:37:37,230
Don't worry, Master Xie. We won't ask anything of you.

504
00:37:37,230 --> 00:37:39,310
It'll just be footage of your daily life.

505
00:37:39,310 --> 00:37:40,700
I'm not good with words.

506
00:37:40,700 --> 00:37:43,280
- Xia Xia.
- A'Yao, how about this?

507
00:37:43,280 --> 00:37:44,930
Look at this face of mine.

508
00:37:44,930 --> 00:37:48,090
Who'd even watch me? I'm bad with words.

509
00:37:48,090 --> 00:37:50,190
You heard her. It'll be footage of your daily life.

510
00:37:50,190 --> 00:37:52,580
You don't have to do anything. They'll do the editing.

511
00:37:52,580 --> 00:37:55,530
I don't want to be filmed. It's pointless.

512
00:37:56,230 --> 00:37:58,200
Stop it! Turn it off!

513
00:37:58,200 --> 00:38:01,360
Do you hear me? Turn that off! You...

514
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:04,520
Look at him. He's only interested in making videos.

515
00:38:04,520 --> 00:38:06,460
If you had channeled this energy into wood carving,

516
00:38:06,460 --> 00:38:08,810
your skills wouldn't be so horrible.

517
00:38:09,280 --> 00:38:10,960
Master, I love you.

518
00:38:16,670 --> 00:38:19,450
Get lost. Silly boy.

519
00:38:19,460 --> 00:38:22,270
Stop filming! Turn it off! Look at him.

520
00:38:22,270 --> 00:38:23,540
- Take a seat.
- Preposterous.

521
00:38:23,540 --> 00:38:26,100
- Uncle, sit down.
- He gets sidetracked so easily.

522
00:38:27,070 --> 00:38:28,560
Excellent!

