539
00:39:22,880 --> 00:39:25,210
Granny Caiyun, it's okay if you can't read it.

540
00:39:25,210 --> 00:39:26,860
I'll explain it to you later.

541
00:39:26,860 --> 00:39:28,590
It's very simple.

542
00:39:28,590 --> 00:39:31,980
This manual lists instructions for new employee mentorship,

543
00:39:31,980 --> 00:39:35,960
assessment, wages, vacations, insurance,

544
00:39:35,960 --> 00:39:38,520
and leaving of post.

545
00:39:38,520 --> 00:39:40,460
You have to abide by these rules.

546
00:39:40,460 --> 00:39:42,490
There's even an attendance bonus!

547
00:39:42,490 --> 00:39:44,780
What does that mean?

548
00:39:44,780 --> 00:39:47,310
An attendance bonus is a monetary reward

549
