550
00:39:51,280 --> 00:39:55,140
Granny, the attendance bonus is ¥200 per month!

551
00:39:55,140 --> 00:39:57,700
¥200?

552
00:39:57,700 --> 00:40:00,400
What if there's an emergency?

553
00:40:00,400 --> 00:40:02,030
The manual states the details clearly.

554
00:40:02,030 --> 00:40:04,500
You can ask for leave three times a month.

555
00:40:04,500 --> 00:40:07,680
If your leave doesn't exceed three times, you can still get your attendance bonus.

556
00:40:07,680 --> 00:40:10,230
Take leave four times or more and you'll lose it.

557
00:40:10,230 --> 00:40:13,360
Your wage will also be deducted based on the time you leave.

558
00:40:13,360 --> 00:40:15,580
If you want the attendance bonus,

559
00:40:15,580 --> 00:40:18,400
